reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This has a high percentage of vitamin E, and it’s manufactured in the USA… win win!
reviews.reviewText: I really like that this is manufactured in the USA and third-party tested. If you zoom in on one of images, you will see this “OUR MANUFACTURER IS FDA REGISTERED AND CERTIFIED BY 3RD PARTY AUDIT”. I included that Imogen my pictures. These small gel pills contain 1200% of our recommended daily allowance of vitamin E. They are easy to swallow and leave no aftertaste. I like that they are supposed to help with our immune system, especially with so much going around right now, and with stress. I’m sure we all deal with stress. I just started using them so I have not used them long enough to see results yet but I’m looking forward to them.
